dc_title_s: South America, Venezuela, plans in Maracaibo Channel (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the National Imagery and Mapping Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "From Venezuelan charts to 1995." Not distributed to depository libraries. "Copyright 1998 by the United States Government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Includes source diagram. Map no.24484. This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
